    )
Maintainer: Lucas Gelape <lucas@voltdata.info>
Description: This package gives a set of functions to extract data from the API of 
    Fogo Cruzado's data repository of shootings in Brazil (https://api.fogocruzado.org.br/).
    Currently, the repository contains geocoded data from shootings and gun shots fired
    in the metropolitan areas of Rio de Janeiro (since July 2016) and Recife (since April 2018).
